    <title>
Tax relief for third-level fees
</title>
    
    <meta name="description" content="Tax relief is available in respect of tuition fees paid in private third-level institutions, in institutions abroad and by repeat students and part-time students. The Student Contribution may also qualify for relief.">
    
    
